source: TEXT_LUCKTA521_04050_SEQ_00<tab>The doomsaying dwarf wishes to send you to gather machine parts─and definitely not to your doom.
target: TEXT_LUCKTA521_04050_SEQ_00<tab>Le villageois désespéré a un travail à vous confier.

source: TEXT_LUCKTA521_04050_TODO_00<tab>Obtain salvage in the Copied Factory.
target: TEXT_LUCKTA521_04050_TODO_00<tab>Récupérer des carcasses de formes de vie mécaniques, dans la réplique de l'usine désaffectée

source: TEXT_LUCKTA521_04050_TODO_01<tab>Deliver the salvage to the doomsaying dwarf.
target: TEXT_LUCKTA521_04050_TODO_01<tab>Remettre les carcasses de formes de vie mécaniques au villageois désespéré, à Komra

source: TEXT_LUCKTA521_04050_VILLAGERD03954_000_001<tab>Ready to go to your doom─er...I mean, get to work, are you? Good, good.
target: TEXT_LUCKTA521_04050_VILLAGERD03954_000_001<tab>Hum. Le porion, il a dit que je pouvais te demander ton aide, alors... c'est ce que je vais faire.

source: TEXT_LUCKTA521_04050_VILLAGERD03954_000_002<tab>As per the chief's instructions, your task is to gather items the machines left behind that might prove useful for rebuilding our village.
target: TEXT_LUCKTA521_04050_VILLAGERD03954_000_002<tab>Son idée à lui, c'est de réutiliser la technologie de ceux qui nous ont attaqués. Moi, je veux bien essayer, mais pour ça, il faudrait d'abord que j'étudie la chose de plus près.

source: TEXT_LUCKTA521_04050_VILLAGERD03954_000_003<tab>Do you know any suitable places for this?
target: TEXT_LUCKTA521_04050_VILLAGERD03954_000_003<tab>Bref, ce serait vraiment chouette que tu me rapportes quelques-unes de leurs machines.

source: TEXT_LUCKTA521_04050_A1_000_001<tab>The machines have a base deep in the tunnels.
target: TEXT_LUCKTA521_04050_A1_000_001<tab>Je peux tenter ma chance au fond des ruines mécaniques, là où se trouvaient nos ennemis.

source: TEXT_LUCKTA521_04050_A1_000_002<tab>There's a ruined factory strewn with machina.
target: TEXT_LUCKTA521_04050_A1_000_002<tab>Je connais une sorte d'usine où je devrais pouvoir trouver ça.

source: TEXT_LUCKTA521_04050_VILLAGERD03954_000_006<tab>While you're out there searching, I'll get my tools ready for dismantling.
target: TEXT_LUCKTA521_04050_VILLAGERD03954_000_006<tab>Parfait<var 1D /var>! Pendant ce temps, je vais aller chercher mes pinces, mes tournevis et tout le reste.

source: TEXT_LUCKTA521_04050_VILLAGERD03954_000_010<tab>I look forward to seeing the spoils of your foray!
target: TEXT_LUCKTA521_04050_VILLAGERD03954_000_010<tab>J'attendrai que tu me rapportes des machines à désosser. Allez, à plus tard<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_LUCKTA521_04050_VILLAGERD03954_000_050<tab>How goes the search? I stand ready to dismantle the spoils of your foray!
target: TEXT_LUCKTA521_04050_VILLAGERD03954_000_050<tab>J'attendrai que tu me rapportes des machines à désosser. Allez, à plus tard<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_LUCKTA521_04050_VILLAGERD03954_000_100<tab>Well, drench my beard, I've never seen anything like this... It's not going to suddenly spring to life and strangle me, is it?
target: TEXT_LUCKTA521_04050_VILLAGERD03954_000_100<tab>Ouah... Effectivement, ça ressemble à rien de connu... Ça va pas me sauter au visage, hein<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_LUCKTA521_04050_VILLAGERD03954_000_101<tab>No? Well, if you're sure... I'll set about studying it at once.
target: TEXT_LUCKTA521_04050_VILLAGERD03954_000_101<tab>Eh bien, merci beaucoup. Je vais pouvoir passer à ma partie préférée<var 1D /var>: le désossage<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_LUCKTA521_04050_VILLAGERD03954_000_102<tab>Oh, I should mention that the chief was looking for you. Seems he has news to share. It's something dreadful, I shouldn't doubt...
target: TEXT_LUCKTA521_04050_VILLAGERD03954_000_102<tab>Ah au fait, le porion te cherchait. Il doit avoir du nouveau pour toi. Passe le voir dès que possible.

source: TEXT_LUCKTA521_04050_VILLAGERD03954_000_105<tab>Have you spoken with the chief yet? Seems he has news to share. It's something dreadful, I shouldn't doubt...
target: TEXT_LUCKTA521_04050_VILLAGERD03954_000_105<tab>Le porion te cherchait. Passe le voir dès que possible.

source: TEXT_LUCKTA521_04050_VILLAGERD03954_000_150<tab>Hm? Ready for another foray, are you? Well, if it wouldn't be too much of a bother...
target: TEXT_LUCKTA521_04050_VILLAGERD03954_000_150<tab>Dis l'<var 08 E905 ((étrangère)) ((étranger)) /var>, euh... Ça va si je te demande encore un coup de main<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_LUCKTA521_04050_VILLAGERD03954_000_151<tab>Excellent! Let our inexorable march towards failure continue!
target: TEXT_LUCKTA521_04050_VILLAGERD03954_000_151<tab>Super<var 1D /var>! Alors voilà. Les machines ennemies que tu m'as rapportées la dernière fois étaient très in<var 16 /var>té<var 16 /var>res<var 16 /var>santes. Sauf qu'elles tombaient lit<var 16 /var>té<var 16 /var>ra<var 16 /var>le<var 16 /var>ment en miettes... Du coup, j'ai pas pu en tirer beaucoup de pièces intactes.

source: TEXT_LUCKTA521_04050_VILLAGERD03954_000_152<tab>So, do you recall the machina you brought back last time? Unfortunately, they were rather far gone, and I couldn't salvage much of them. Do you think you could bring back more of the same?
target: TEXT_LUCKTA521_04050_VILLAGERD03954_000_152<tab>Tu penses pouvoir aller m'en chercher d'autres<var 1D /var>? Ça m'aiderait vraiment dans mes recherches.

source: TEXT_LUCKTA521_04050_VILLAGERD03954_000_154<tab>Thank you! With the bits from the extra specimens, I think we can put together something useful─even if we're inevitably doomed to fail.
target: TEXT_LUCKTA521_04050_VILLAGERD03954_000_154<tab>Je ferai en sorte que tes efforts ne soient pas vains. Parole de Gogg<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_LUCKTA521_04050_VILLAGERD03954_000_155<tab>Please bring me more of the same machina as last time. With the bits from the extra specimens, I think we can put together something useful─even if we're inevitably doomed to fail.
target: TEXT_LUCKTA521_04050_VILLAGERD03954_000_155<tab>Je me ferai un plaisir d'étudier les machines que tu me rapporteras, et d'en tirer la substantifique moelle<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_LUCKTA521_04050_VILLAGERD03954_000_250<tab>Ah, yes, precisely the same as last time! This ought to suffice for our purposes, thank you!
target: TEXT_LUCKTA521_04050_VILLAGERD03954_000_250<tab>Ah, de belles machines déglinguées comme je les aime<var 1D /var>! Ça devrait faire l'affaire, merci.

source: TEXT_LUCKTA521_04050_VILLAGERD03954_000_251<tab>You know, I've been feeling a little bit more optimistic in spite of myself. By keeping occupied with our work, I find my mind doesn't stray towards the doom and gloom as often as it used to. Seems it's better to take action than being idle with negative thoughts.
target: TEXT_LUCKTA521_04050_VILLAGERD03954_000_251<tab>C'est drôle, mais je ressens comme une forme de paix intérieure quand je démonte des trucs... Le travail manuel, un remède efficace contre la déprime<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_LUCKTA521_04050_VILLAGERD03954_000_252<tab>If only it weren't so hard to take action in the first place...
target: TEXT_LUCKTA521_04050_VILLAGERD03954_000_252<tab>Tu me diras, c'est pas toujours facile de se secouer quand on est au fond du trou...

source: TEXT_LUCKTA521_04050_VILLAGERD03954_000_253<tab>Well, I should be getting back to my work. Perhaps you could report to the chief, in case he has other tasks that want doing. Thanks again for bringing the parts!
target: TEXT_LUCKTA521_04050_VILLAGERD03954_000_253<tab>Grâce à toi, je vais pouvoir me mettre à fond dans mes recherches. Je n'ai plus besoin d'aide, mais peut-être que le porion aura d'autres tâches à te confier.
